<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>other on Yilin Miao</title><link>https://miaoyl.work/categories/other/</link><description>Recent content in other on Yilin Miao</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Jul 2020 17:41:49 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://miaoyl.work/categories/other/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>沉默是金</title><link>https://miaoyl.work/post/silenceisgold/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jul 2020 17:41:49 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://miaoyl.work/post/silenceisgold/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>沉默是金，拼音是chén mò shì jīn，意思是指不常说话的人易取得成功。出自《&lt;a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%AD%C2%B7%E4%B8%BA%E6%94%BF">论语·为政&lt;/a>》子张学干禄。子曰：“多闻阙疑，慎言其余，则寡尤；多见阙殆，慎行其余，则寡悔。言寡尤，行寡悔，禄在其中矣！”&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>一万年都有左中右</title><link>https://miaoyl.work/post/leftandright/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2020 22:07:49 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://miaoyl.work/post/leftandright/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>除了沙漠，凡有人群的地方，都有左、中、右，一万年以后还会是这样。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>毛泽东 - 《毛泽东选集》第五卷，人民出版社1977年4月第1版（一九五七年五月十五日文章&lt;em>事情正在其变化&lt;/em>）&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>波洛涅斯的劝诫</title><link>https://miaoyl.work/post/polonius/</link><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2019 21:41:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://miaoyl.work/post/polonius/</guid><description>&lt;p>哈姆雷特里的雷欧提斯(Laertes)去法国之前，他老爹波洛涅斯(Polonius)给他的人生劝诫:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>又建博客了</title><link>https://miaoyl.work/post/first/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2019 21:14:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://miaoyl.work/post/first/</guid><description>&lt;p>上次开博客是5年前，这次光域名就直接买了十年，算是个LTS版本？🤣&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>